   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Children In Foster Care Heal.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Several days after the Sandy Hook elementary school shooting, AIW reached out to the counselors and the traumatized children of Newtown Ct. AIW donated 500 Comfort Penguins. Our &quot;Therapeutic Penguins&quot; were passed out by local counselors to children in need. We received overwhelming responses regarding how therapeutically-healing our crisis penguin was from counselors and parents who&apos;s children suffered through one of America&apos;s darkest tragedies. Foster Care Children Need Our Comfort Penguin Too!</narrative>
  </description>
